OL,3,CMum admits stealing #15,000 from two
OL,4,Cresidents while working at care home
OL,6,FA Carlisle woman is due to be
OL,7,Fsentenced by a judge next month for
OL,8,Fstealing thousands of pounds from two
OL,9,Fpensioners while working at a city
OL,10,Fcare home.
OL,12,FThirty-year-old Jessica Gregson
OL,13,Fappeared in front of magistrates on 4
OL,14,FJuly 2025.
OL,16,FDuring a short hearing, Gregson
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to two offences.
