OL,6,FShe admitted using that woman's card
OL,7,Fwithout permission and stealing
OL,8,F#6,140.50 from her between 1 December
OL,9,F2023 and 7 February the following year.
OL,11,FIt was when Gregson appeared at
OL,12,FCarlisle Crown Court in May in
OL,13,Frelation to those original two charges
OL,14,Fthat a judge learned there may be a
OL,15,Fsecond victim. Relatives of that man `
OL,16,Fwho has since died ` were present in
OL,17,Fcourt on that occasion.
