OL,6,FThe case was adjourned at that stage
OL,7,Ffor further enquiries to be made. As a
OL,8,Fresult, two additional charges were
OL,9,Fbrought and these were admitted in
OL,10,Fcourt today.
OL,12,F"Miss Gregson was working in a care
OL,13,Fhome," prosecutor Diane Jackson said
OL,14,Fduring this morning's hearing.
OL,16,F"This (criminal conduct) is in
OL,17,Frelation to two of the residents."
